title: SMNTY Double Feature: Suspiria
itunes:title: SMNTY Double Feature: Suspiria
description:
In this very special double feature episode, we compare and contrast the two versions of the film Suspiria, and talk colors, dance, witches, motherhood, corruption, death and final girls. We also ask the question is Tilda Swinton everyone?! Mother of sighs!
